PLACEHOLDER: This file needs to be replaced with an actual PNG icon.

Required icon specifications:
- Format: PNG with transparency (RGBA)
- Size: 256x256 pixels (primary), with additional sizes at 16, 32, 48, 64, 128, 512 for best results
- Design suggestion: A stylized document/editor icon with the letters "OE" or a pen/cursor motif
- Colors: Consider a modern gradient (e.g., blue-to-purple) on a rounded-rectangle background
- For macOS, also generate an .icns file from the PNG source
- For Windows, also generate an .ico file from the PNG source

To generate a proper icon from an SVG or high-res PNG:
  - Linux: Use ImageMagick: convert icon-512.png -resize 256x256 icon.png
  - macOS .icns: Use iconutil with an .iconset directory
  - Windows .ico: Use ImageMagick: convert icon-512.png -define icon:auto-resize=256,128,64,48,32,16 icon.ico
